Emitting both a sound and a flash, this system provides both audible and visual feedback, supplying information about which stage a system is at and helping to identify and diagnose faults with data that can be passed to a plumber for investigation.

Title: Scalemaster Magnetic Gold magnetic 22mm Gold
Description: Protecting individual appliances, the Scalemaster Magnetic Gold 22mm limescale inhibitor prevents limescale build-up by influencing the crystal structure of limescale. Harnessing the results of laboratory research, which has shown that the growth of limescale crystals can be affected by a magnetic field, this inhibitor uses magnet technology to adapt forming crystals into needle-shaped aragonite. This aragonite is less damaging than the more commonly seen calcite, and is less likely to stick hard to the surfaces of heat exchangers.
